Enum StaggeredHorizontalGrid.SGridPadding

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing interface:
    StaggeredHorizontalGrid

    public static enum StaggeredHorizontalGrid.SGridPadding
extends Enum<StaggeredHorizontalGrid.SGridPadding>
    A staggered grid will consist of cells which are defined as being between the nodes of the original grid. The cell centres are at the midpoints of the nodes of the original grid. Whether or not these cells extend beyond the original grid is defined by the padding. The defined paddings for StaggeredHorizontalGrids are:
    • LOW
    • HIGH
    • BOTH
    • NO_PADDING
    • NO_OFFSET
    Author:
    Guy Griffiths
